                    <b>I</b> &nbsp; <u> @Model.From_Name</u> &nbsp; <b>S/O, W/O</b> &nbsp; <u>@Model.From_FatherName</u>  &nbsp; <b>CNIC-NICOP</b> &nbsp; <u>@Model.From_CNIC_NICOP</u> &nbsp;
