                    &nbsp; <u>@Model.Plot_Size</u> &nbsp; <b>Want to sell my Plot to</b> &nbsp; <u>@Model.To_Name</u> <br />
                    <b>Please issue No Demand Certificate NDC for this Plot.(NDC will be issued within 5 working days).</b>
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <table cellspacing="0" border="0" style="width:1000px;font-size: 19px;margin: 5px 0 40px 0">
        <tr>
            <td width="1000px" align="left" valign=bottom style="font-weight:bold">I HEREBY CONFIRM THAT TILL DATE, ALL THE INSTALLMENTS HAVE BEEN PAID & NO DUES ARE PENDING.</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <table cellspacing="0" border="0" style="width:1000px;font-size: 22px;">
        <tr>
